Simple one player battleship game written in Java SDK8.
It's a 10x10 grid with 2 Destroyers( length 4) and one Battleship( length 5)
How to play:
Either open it with an IntelliJ and run or:
1. Open cmd
2. go to folder with Game.java
3. in console type: java Game.java
4. First give the row number from 0-9
5. Second give a column letter with Caps Lock from A-J

If all ships are destroyed the game ends.